{"text_id":21128,"tokens":["The"," limitations"," of"," our"," brains"," in"," visualizing"," more"," than"," three"," dimensions"," are"," deeply"," rooted"," in"," both"," biological"," and"," cognitive"," factors","."," Our"," brains"," are"," wired"," to"," process"," information"," in"," a"," spatially"," constrained"," environment",","," and"," this"," restriction"," hinders"," our"," ability"," to"," visualize"," higher","-","dimensional"," objects",".","\n\n","The"," visual"," cortex"," in"," our"," brains"," is"," primarily"," responsible"," for"," processing"," visual"," information"," from"," the"," eyes"," and"," translating"," it"," into"," a"," mental"," representation"," of"," the"," world","."," This"," cortex"," is"," tuned"," to"," interpret"," visual"," information"," in"," the"," context"," of"," our"," three","-","dimensional"," environment",","," making"," it"," adept"," at"," recognizing"," and"," manipulating"," objects"," within"," this"," dimension","."," However",","," it"," struggles"," to"," grasp"," the"," complexities"," of"," objects"," that"," exist"," in"," more"," than"," three"," dimensions",".","\n\n","Moreover",","," our"," brains"," have"," evolved"," to"," prioritize"," the"," processing"," of"," information"," that"," is"," relevant"," to"," our"," immediate"," surroundings","."," This"," focus"," on"," three"," dimensions"," is"," reflected"," in"," the"," organization"," of"," brain"," regions"," involved"," in"," visual"," processing"," and"," spatial"," navigation","."," These"," regions"," are"," optimized"," for"," representing"," objects"," and"," environments"," that"," exist"," in"," our"," physical"," reality",".","\n\n","Furthermore",","," the"," very"," concept"," of"," \"","visualization","\""," is"," inherently"," limited"," by"," our"," three","-","dimensional"," perspective","."," It"," is"," challenging"," for"," us"," to"," mentally"," rotate"," or"," manipulate"," objects"," in"," a"," way"," that"," transcends"," the"," constraints"," of"," our"," physical"," world","."," This"," limitation"," may"," be"," why"," it"," is"," difficult"," for"," us"," to"," visualize"," objects"," that"," exist"," in"," more"," than"," three"," dimensions",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," the"," limitations"," of"," our"," brains"," in"," visualizing"," more"," than"," three"," dimensions"," is"," a"," result"," of"," a"," combination"," of"," biological"," constraints",","," cognitive"," limitations",","," and"," the"," inherent"," dimensionality"," of"," our"," visual"," experience","."],"sub_source":"reddit","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}